    "chemicalDescription": [
      "sh-Oligopeptide-1 Tripeptide-58 Hexapeptide-40 Decapeptide-41 sr-Spider Polypeptide-3 is a single chain recombinant fusion peptide produced by fermentation in  E. coli.  The starting gene is synthesized by the fusion of the gene from sh-Oligopeptide-1, Tripeptide-58, Hexapeptide-40,  Decapeptide-41, and sr-Spider Polypeptide-3 . The fusion peptide contains 186 amino acids which may contain disulfide bonds and/or glycosylation, and consists of the proper sequence of the 20 standard amino acids."
